Sharon Stone, 64, stole the show once again at the Cannes Film Festival 2022. The actress donned a beautiful bejewelled emerald gown as she walked the red carpet on Monday evening. She was attending the screening of Crimes Of The Future at Palais des Festivals.Sharon was the epitome of glamour in the strapless dress.The garment was adorned with hundreds of beads which sparkled as the Basic Instinct actress posed for cameras.Sharon’s floor-length dress featured a daring thigh-high split which showcased her toned legs.The ensemble also had a flattering ruching detail which drew attention to Sharon’s slim waist.The iconic actress paired the look with some matching green heels and gold sparkly earrings.Her short blonde hair was kept off her face and the look was finished with red lipstick and demure eye makeup.